Class Diagram

java.lang.Object
org.example.scdpro2.business.models.Diagram
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
Direct Known Subclasses:
BClassBox, PackageClassComponent, PackageComponent
public abstract class Diagram extends Object implements Serializable
Abstract class representing a diagram within a project. This class serves as the base class for different types of diagrams (such as class diagrams, package diagrams, etc.) in the system. It provides common properties and methods that all diagram types should have, including a title and methods for rendering the diagram and generating code.
